    "_scoring_notes": "Scoring:The 1-2 scores were coded 1; 3-4 scores were coded 2; 5-6 scores were coded 3; 7-8 scores were coded 4. The cognitive restraint scale was composed of items 2, 11, 12, 15, 16, and 18. The uncontrolled eating scale was composed of items 1, 4, 5, 7, 8, 9, 13, 14, and 17. The emotional eating scale was composed of items 3, 6, and 10.",
